text: Kingdom of Armenia may mean: *Kingdom of Armenia (Antiquity) also known as Artaxiad or Arsacid Armenia, 190 BC to AD 387/428 *Kingdom of Armenia (Middle Ages) also known as Bagratid Armenia, AD 885 to 1045 sometimes also called "Kingdom of Armenia" or "Armenian kingdom" are: *Satrapy of Armenia also known as Orontid Armenia *the Armenian Kingdom of Cilicia, 1198 to 1375 *Kingdom of Artsakh *Kingdom of Commagene *Kingdom of Sophene *Kingdom of Vaspurakan
title: Kingdom of Armenia
